        public Shipment withPriceAdjustments(Map<ProductType,PriceAdjustment> priceAdjustments)
        Allows you to adjust the prices that are returned. Announced by setting the map of production descriptions and the corresponding price adjustment. Note that price adjustment is made on the price without VAT.
